In terms of deployment, the shift towards cloud-based NLP solutions is gaining traction due to the scalability, flexibility, and cost-effectiveness they offer. Cloud-based deployment models provide businesses with agility and access to advanced NLP capabilities without the need for extensive infrastructure investments or maintenance. On-premises deployment options, while offering higher control and security, are better suited for industries with specific data governance requirements or strict compliance protocols.

